title: Watered Down
author: VD
content_html:
You can’t say I didn’t warn you. But you shouldn’t be surprised, because conservatives don’t ever play to win.

The final audit reports from Cyber Ninjas work in Maricopa County Arizona were released over the weekend. They appear watered down. What was removed?

In the final report, the statement calling for decertification was eliminated.

First, you can’t revive a corpse. Second, you’re not going to vote your way out of this. That ship sailed sometime between 1965 and 1980.
